description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 69, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 138, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 5 for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10692-75770-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [138 Votes, Top 15% Score]
